headline: Raymond James Upgrade and Organic Growth Story Might Change The Case For Investing In Stryker (SYK)
summary: Recently, Raymond James upgraded Stryker to “Outperform,” highlighting its track record of 10%-plus organic revenue growth and positioning in medical technology across orthopedics, surgical tools, neurotechnology, and patient care. The upgrade underscores how Stryker’s consistent organic expansion and perceived quality within its sector are influencing how analysts reassess its prospects relative to peers.
